I"÷<p>I‚Äôm on a quest to reduce my principles in life to utter simplicity.</p>

<p>Here‚Äôs what I have boiled it down to so far:</p>

<ol>
  <li><strong>MAKE EVERYTHING SIMPLE</strong>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://isene.org/onepagebooks/#1pb-12-make-it-simple">Reduce everything</a> to <a href="https://isene.org/2020/02/Simple.html">only what is needed</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>‚ÄúDO THAT WHICH HELPS. DON‚ÄôT DO THAT WHICH DOESN‚ÄôT HELP.‚Äù</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Focus on what you can control
        <ul>
          <li>Pick what <a href="https://isene.org/2019/02/Exciting.html">excites</a> you and do that</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Don‚Äôt spend energy on what you cannot control
        <ul>
          <li>Disregard the past &amp; much of the future (practice improvisation)</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>BE <a href="https://isene.org/2018/09/Podcast-EasilyHurt.html">INTERESTED</a></strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Learn to <a href="https://isene.org/2018/11/Podcast-MentalTraining.html">do nothing</a> - be <a href="https://isene.org/onepagebooks/#1pb-2-mental-training---the-core">present</a> - <a href="https://isene.org/onepagebooks/#1pb-6-listening---superpower">listen</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>GIVE <a href="https://isene.org/2018/11/Podcast-Impress.html">MORE PLUSSES</a></strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Be <a href="https://isene.org/2018/12/Podcast-MeaningOfLife.html">empathetic</a> - <a href="https://isene.org/2018/10/Podcast-HelpOthers.html">help others</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>ENJOY <a href="https://isene.org/onepagebooks/#1pb-13-game-review-life">THE GAME</a></strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Challenge yourself on the <a href="https://isene.org/2020/03/RALE.html">RALE scale</a> - learn to enjoy as much as possible by moving on the scale
        <ul>
          <li>R = Resist</li>
          <li>A = Accept</li>
          <li>L = Like</li>
          <li>E = Enjoy</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

